Idea
Help miners figure out profitability based on transacions from dogecoind and
exchange rates from 3 exchages.

BASICS
whenever gem for schediling
generator for setting project up
 * Includes rake db create, rake db:migrate, set up user
 * May cp dogecoin.conf over to config
dogecoind binary
Transactions table tracking all incoming and outgoing items for user
configuration for which coins being mined/preferred
settings panel for choosing coins
START WITH DOGE, move to litecoin and bitcoin after
D3 for graphing
Ask for upfront cost and monthly electrical cost

Get some information from following data sources:
http://bter.com/api
https://vircurex.com/welcome/api?locale=en
https://www.cryptsy.com/pages/api
